==Quotes==
*Motormouth Maybelle: "If we get any more white people in here, this is gonna be a suburb."

*Wilbur Turnblad (to Tracy): "This is America, you gotta be big to think big."
Edna Turnblad: "Big ain't the problem in this family, Wilbur."

*Edna Turnblad: "Don't test me Tracy Turnblad, my diet pill's wearin' off!"

*Tracy Turnblad (to Wilbur): "Dancing on that show is my dream!"

*Link Larkin: "Wanna be one of the Nicest Kids in Town? Cut school tomorrow and come to audition!"

*Penny Pingleton (to Tracy): "Oh. Your hair deflated."

*Council Members (duirng 'Nicest Kids in Town'): "Roll Call! I'm Amber! Brad! Tammy! Fender! Brenda! Sketch! Shelley! IQ! LuAnne! Joey! Mikey! Vicki! Becky! Bix! Jessie! Darla! Paulie! Noreen! Doreen! And I'm... Link!"

==Trivia==
